## Fixes Performed
- **Restored [IQRHRPVerifier.sol](file:///c:/Users/mergetoken/contracts/IQRHRPVerifier.sol)**: This interface file was missing and prevented compilation. I restored it.
- **Fixed OpenZeppelin Imports**: Updated imports in `LPStaking`, `MergeCoreManager`, `StakingPool`, and `MerkleBooster` to be compatible with OpenZeppelin v5 (`security/ReentrancyGuard.sol` -> `utils/ReentrancyGuard.sol`).
- **Fixed [GovernanceSimple.sol](file:///c:/Users/mergetoken/contracts/GovernanceSimple.sol)**: Fixed a syntax error in struct instantiation.
